      </p>

      <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:40px;">
        <span style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#4B5563; background:#1A1A1A; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:20px;">Module 1: Gap Report (2 min)</span>
