      <h3 style="font-family:Georgia,serif; font-size:22px; color:#0D0D0D; margin:40px 0 8px;">Root Cause Identification</h3>
      <div class="apn-r-divider" style="width:40px; height:2px;"></div>
      <p class="apn-r-body">Based on your score and your tier, your most likely root cause is one of four sub-gaps. Select the one that best describes your pattern. This becomes the primary focus of your Week 1 protocol.</p>

      <div class="apn-r-subgap-options" id="apn-rec-subgaps">
