          <p class="apn-r-body" style="margin:0;">Add turmeric with black pepper with your dinner. One product. Do not add colostrum this week. Evaluate for 7 days. Focus on whether your joint soreness between sessions changes. That is your signal that the NF-kB inhibition is working.</p>
