          <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:3px; color:#F59E0B; margin-bottom:8px;">COMPETITOR THIS WEEK</p>
          <p class="apn-r-body" style="margin:0;">Colostrum in the morning and turmeric with dinner. Both this week. Eliminate alcohol for the week. Compare your soreness log from Week 1 to this week. The combination of protein timing, active recovery, and the anti-inflammatory stack should produce a measurable difference in DOMS duration by day 5 or 6.</p>
