          <p style="font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:3px; color:#EF4444; margin-bottom:8px;">CHAMPION THIS WEEK</p>
          <p class="apn-r-body" style="margin:0;">Evaluate every protocol element and rank by measured impact. Keep the top four as your permanent recovery infrastructure. Anything that has not produced measurable improvement in HRV, soreness, or performance can be rotated out. Build the leanest possible system that delivers complete recovery. Complexity without data is not precision. It is noise.</p>
