  <!-- MODULE 6: 30-DAY CHALLENGE -->
  <div class="apn-r-section" id="apn-rec-m6" style="background:#0D0D0D;">
    <div class="apn-r-inner">
      <span class="apn-r-label">THE COMMITMENT</span>
      <h2 class="apn-r-headline apn-r-headline--white">The Gap Closes When You Decide It Does</h2>
      <div class="apn-r-divider"></div>

      <p class="apn-r-body apn-r-body--white" style="margin-bottom:40px;">Four habits. 30 days. Measurable outcomes. No guessing whether the work is paying off.</p>

      <div style="margin-bottom:40px;">
        <div class="apn-r-habit-item">
          <div class="apn-r-habit-item__num">01</div>
          <div class="apn-r-habit-item__text">
            <strong>25 to 30g of protein within 45 minutes of every training session, every time.</strong> Prepare the shaker before you leave for training. This is not a decision made after the session. The decision was already made. You are just executing it.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="apn-r-habit-item">
          <div class="apn-r-habit-item__num">02</div>
          <div class="apn-r-habit-item__text">
            <strong>20-minute active recovery session on every rest day.</strong> Walk, bike, swim, or move at 50 to 60% effort. Scheduled on the calendar before the week starts. Not optional based on how you feel.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="apn-r-habit-item">
          <div class="apn-r-habit-item__num">03</div>
          <div class="apn-r-habit-item__text">
            <strong>Morning HRV reading every single day.</strong> Immediately upon waking. Log the number. At the end of each week, calculate your 7-day average. Let the trend drive your training intensity decisions, not your emotions.
          </div>
